. Just wipe it on and sleep. The formula absorbs instantly—leaving <strong>no greasy</strong> residue on your pillow—and works with your body's natural repair cycle overnight. You wake up looking tight while the cream does the heavy lifting.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0ZUVz69s3_text","label":"gg0ZUVz69s3_text","default":"<span style=\"font-size:25px;\">3. </span><span style=\"color:#0055B5;font-size:25px;\">FORMULATED</span><span style=\"font-size:25px;\"> IN ITALY &amp; BACKED BY DERMATOLOGIST</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeNNIcscpb_text","label":"ggeNNIcscpb_text","default":"<span style=\"font-size:31px;\">3. </span><span style=\"color:#0055B5;font-size:31px;\">FORMULATED</span><span style=\"font-size:31px;\"> IN ITALY &amp; BACKED BY DERMATOLOGIST</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYNTDnIV-v_text","label":"ggYNTDnIV-v_text","default":"<p>Forget mass-produced factory lotions. Omnis is crafted in <strong>small family-owned lab</strong> in Italy under <strong>strict European standards</strong>. It delivers &nbsp;structural support specifically designed for men’s thicker, aging skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggePMxEWoNW_text","label":"ggePMxEWoNW_text","default":"4. 60-DAY MONEY-BACK GUARANTEE—<span style=\"color:#0055B5;\">ZERO RISK</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAaxaLLhOx_text","label":"ggAaxaLLhOx_text","default":"4. 60-DAY MONEY-BACK GUARANTEE—<span style=\"color:#0055B5;\">ZERO RISK</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIw617NHz5_text","label":"ggIw617NHz5_text","default":"<p>We take the risk, not you. Use the entire jar. If you don’t see a defined jawline and reduced sagging within <strong>60 days</strong>, we refund you in full. No questions asked. You see results, or you don't pay.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdASef_1a8_text","label":"ggdASef_1a8_text","default":"5. JOIN <span style=\"color:#0055B5;\">THOUSANDS OF MEN</span> WHO LOOK YOUNGER"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkZndGajL__text","label":"ggkZndGajL__text","default":"5. JOIN <span style=\"color:#0055B5;\">THOUSANDS OF MEN</span> WHO LOOK YOUNGER"},{"type":"html","id":"ggM_gYnhezM_text","label":"ggM_gYnhezM_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(254,255,252);color:#0B1F3F;font-size:17.6px;\">This isn’t just a cream; it’s a strategy to stay in the game. Thousands of men have already ditched the \"tired old man\" look for a fresher appearance. Now it’s your turn to look as young as you feel.</span></p>"}],
